article_title: Rep. Heck’s rematch in 10th Congressional District features only one Republican this time
article_text: Only one of U.S. Rep. Denny Heck’s three opponents has much experience in campaigns, and Heck, a politician-turned-wealthy-businessman, is sitting on more than $900,000 in campaign funds with more on the way.
